		{
			dependencies: ["0194FAB6E9EFFA13"]
			description: ["Sleeve Darts are the Tang Sect's most compact weapon — spring-loaded into the sleeve, triggered by wrist snap. Silent, concealable, and deadly at short range. They're the foundation of hidden weapon fighting style: deny the enemy the chance to react before the weapon has already landed. Craft them at the Forging Table from Spirit Iron and compressed steel."]
			id: "4A7C9E2F5B8D1A3C"
