		{
			dependencies: ["0CB6D79172FC5B93"]
			description: ["The Tang Sect's three core techniques define its identity as much as the hidden weapons do. Purple Demon Eyes (P key) — four tiers from night vision to ranged mental damage to full AoE stun domain. Ghost Shadow Track (N key) — three tiers from enhanced dash to 20-block teleport with 35% dodge. Controlling Crane Capturing Dragon (H key) — telekinesis scaled to eight simultaneous targets by mastery. Each technique trains through repeated use. They stack with soul ring active skills."]
			id: "5B8D1F3A6C9E2B4D"
			rewards: [
