		{
			dependencies: ["4A7C9E2F5B8D1A3C"]
			description: ["The Tang Sect's poisons are a parallel doctrine to the hidden weapons — ranked on the same ten-tier scale. Numbing Powder at level one causes temporary muscle paralysis; higher-tier poisons cause organ failure, soul power suppression, and effects that standard healing cannot counter. Poisons are applied to darts and needles or deployed as area powders. The combination of a paralyzed target and a volley of Dragon Beard Needles ends most encounters before they begin."]
			id: "6C9E2A4F7D1B3C5E"
			optional: true
			rewards: [
