		{
			dependencies: ["5B8D1F3A6C9E2B4D"]
			description: ["The Godly Zhuge Crossbow fires 48 bolts in a single volley — the defining area-denial weapon of the Tang Sect. It requires precision construction at the Forging Table using advanced Spirit Iron components and a calibrated mechanism that few cultivators below Spirit Ancestor can fully control. Against clustered enemies or large beasts, a single volley clears the engagement. Combine with Numbing Powder for maximum effect."]
			id: "7D1F3B5A8E2C4D6F"
