		{
			dependencies: ["7D1F3B5A8E2C4D6F"]
			description: ["The Peacock Plume fires 365 spirit energy needles in a fan arc — one for every day of the year, Tang San once claimed. It requires materials beyond what standard Forging Table work produces alone; the resonance needed in the projectile tips demands Spirit Scholar-grade cultivation to impart. Against multiple enemies or a single powerful beast, the Peacock Plume turns a cultivator into a one-volley artillery piece."]
