		{
			dependencies: ["7D1F3B5A8E2C4D6F"]
			description: ["The Continental Tournament pits five-person academy teams against eight novel-accurate opponents across five rounds. Four opponents per round, each with a unique martial soul, element-specific skills, and Spirit Avatar mode when cornered. Rewards scale from crystals to legendary Tang Sect weapons for bracket completion. It is the first structured test of whether your cultivation, hidden weapons, and technique mastery function together under pressure — and the last milestone before the endgame weapons become accessible."]
