		{
			dependencies: ["0194FAB6E9EFFA13"]
			description: ["The Tang Sect outfits its disciples in light, unadorned armor built for speed and concealment rather than raw plating. The full Regalia — helmet, robe, leggings, and boots — is crafted at a standard crafting table from Spirit Steel reinforced with Spirit Iron. It bridges the gap between the early Spirit Cloth set and the Soul Forged plate that GTCEu-era cultivators wear, and it is the expected uniform for anyone practicing hidden weapon doctrine seriously."]
