		{
			dependencies: ["4A7C9E2F5B8D1A3C"]
			description: ["Between the humble Sleeve Dart and the Godly Zhuge Crossbow sits the Tang Sect's working arsenal. The Bone Piercing Needle punches through armor a dart cannot. The Tense Back Flower Crossbow mounts across the shoulders and answers an ambush from behind with a full volley. The Powder Shooting Shadow carries the sect's poisons to targets well outside throwing range. Each is forged at the Forging Table as your rank climbs — collect all three to round out your concealed loadout."]
