		{
			dependencies: ["4B84D5A3ED42C784"]
			description: ["The Sect Inheritance Token marks a cultivator as a full inheritor of Tang Sect doctrine. It is assembled from a Nine Petal Jade Lotus, Jade Phosphor Moss, Heaven Blue Vine, an Immortal Herb, a Spirit Iron Ingot, and two Soul Crystals — rare herbs from the deepest Qi zones of the Spirit Beast Forest combined with endgame crafting material. Producing one proves you have mastered herb gathering, alchemy-grade botany, and soul crystal acquisition in equal measure."]
