		{
			dependencies: ["23D5469DF20A7E80"]
			description: ["Yama's Invitation and Bodhi Blood are the Tang Sect's two legendary hidden weapons — each destroyed in the act of use, each capable of deciding a fight against opponents far above your rank. They cannot be forged; they drop only from the most powerful sources in the world. Holding both at once is the final collector's milestone of hidden weapon doctrine. Spend them wisely: a one-use weapon saved forever is a weapon wasted."]
