		{
			description: ["Iron's Spells & Spellbooks puts spellcasting in the off-hand for the Cloth armor path. Craft the &eIronbound Tome&r yourself at a crafting table — chains, leather, and paper — this quest only completes when you craft it, not when you loot one. The Tome starts with several spell slots; higher-tier books hold more and cast at greater power. Spell Scrolls drop from enemies, mage towers, and dungeon chests — right-click a scroll while holding your Spellbook to inscribe it permanently. Spells cost Mana, which regenerates passively and scales with Intelligence and Wisdom stat soul investment. For cultivators on the Cloth path, this is your primary damage system alongside soul ring active skills and Tang Sect techniques."]
